title: Ops - Bots
description: This dashboard helps to detect and investigate bot traffic. Detailed breakdowns by bot type, country, request URIs and user agents are also provided.

title: Ops - Snapshot
description: This dashboard provides a high-level overview of the most important Ops log metrics including a breakdown of request and caching details. More detailed metrics by content type, IP, location, protocol, and request method are also provided.

title: Ops - Security
description: This dashboard provides an analysis of Ops threat traffic including the total number of requests and threats stopped. More detailed metrics by country, city, IP, threat type, and user agent are also provided.

title: Ops - Reliability
description: This dashboard provides insights into application/site reliability with an overview of request successes and errors. More details breakdowns by HTTP status codes, and request URIs are also provided.

title: Ops - Performance
description: This dashboard provides an analysis to help identify and resolve performance-related issues. Detailed breakdowns by response time, caching status, content type, host name, request method, protocol, and request URIs are also provided.
